---
// Newsletter sign-up component
---

<section class="newsletter container" aria-label="Newsletter">
  <h2>Dołącz do newslettera SEO & AI</h2>
  <p>Cotygodniowe porady, narzędzia i strategie SEO copywritingu, AI content i GEO — prosto na Twój email.</p>
  <form class="newsletter-form" action="#" method="post">
    <input
      type="email"
      name="email"
      placeholder="Twój adres email..."
      required
      aria-label="Adres email"
    />
    <button type="submit">Zapisz się</button>
  </form>
</section>
